{"tid":1409583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"享受生活每一程，起身搭港鐵啦喂！！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T22:58:21.000Z","uid":231210,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab87ff5e0a8ad42594622588872c3515ff1c0f2","tid":1409583,"uid":231210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:43:17.000Z","msg":"如果你想參與迫爆港鐵行動，請務必穿著整齊上班衣服，千祈唔好著黑衫。<br />\n<br />\n流水社運的精髓就是無名無姓，無可辨認。<br />\n<br />\n著上班衣服，買一張單程票，來回坐上列車，例如你想堵九龍塘站，便不斷來回石峽尾站及樂富站，迫爆車箱，唔駛犯法，嘆住冷氣抗爭。金鐘，荔景，北角係同一做法。<br />\n<br />\n總之，大家盡早出門口，可以就六點，唔得就七點。<br />\n<br />\n流水社運，眾志成城。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"f83fbd276fdc6b934848187be872d3cf26cd87b0","tid":1409583,"uid":231210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c99d72ff02f3fa25eb1674c1cfb0c43202b14cce","tid":1409583,"uid":231210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:45:50.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"c89a7fe57e00e4fb3c57d7bb4f059efcaae7eb4f","tid":1409583,"uid":76975,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:46:08.000Z","msg":"嚴重警告<br />\n咪撚再扮聖人叫人停手<br />\n前線要五花大綁就五花大綁<br />\n要佢剝光豬就剝光豬<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再比我聽到唔好打<br />\n<br />\n認同 推上熱門"},{"pid":"ae02147b6c18ccd07cb29bf8eaeec8949387d615","tid":1409583,"uid":231210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:46:11.000Z","msg":"係時間起身搭港鐵"},{"pid":"54ec7c1395984837e8659b50b15d047483b693ef","tid":1409583,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:46:48.000Z","msg":"起身喇喂，令更多人被動罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aba9ea3c2c03578074772ce9ad7d8653bcb3caa","tid":1409583,"uid":231210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:05.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"aa323082dd53ba2455e3e2995125bb792de99570","tid":1409583,"uid":231210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco